            "section_content_text_hXHk9L": {
              "type": "_section-content__text",
              "settings": {
                "text": "<p>We've partnered with Ecologi and the Eden Reforestation Project to rebuild Madagascar's mangrove forests. We're doing this by planting a tree for every game sold on the Big Potato website.Mangroves are four times better at removing carbon from the atmosphere than rainforests. But with nearly 90% of Madagascar's original forests gone, it's important that we try to reverse deforestation. This way, we can support both the environment and the local community.</p>",
