            "section_content_text_etJDA3": {
              "type": "_section-content__text",
              "settings": {
                "text": "<p>We realized that an easy way to reduce our carbon footprint was to package our games in smaller boxes.<br/><br/>The pieces inside are exactly the same, so you get just as much game as before, but the smaller size means we can reduce pollution from transportation by fitting more of our games into ships and trucks.<br/><br/>Plus, there's the added bonus of being able to fit more games on your shelf, too!</p>",
