              "type": "_section-content__text",
              "settings": {
                "text": "<p>There's too much plastic in the world, so we try to avoid it wherever possible. We're not there yet, but by the end of 2021, we plan to make 64% of our games plastic-free.<br/><br/>We're doing this by removing the shrink wrap around boxes and cards, replacing our plastic stickers with cellulose, and removing all our plastic inserts.<br/><br/>We've branded all of our eco-friendly games with a Plastic-Free Whale, so if you see it on the box, it means you're looking at a genuine, plastic-free party starter.</p>",
